  "texts": [
    "This review also investigated the features, perceived credibility, and usability of DMHIs during waiting times.",
    "Methods:In this systematic review, we searched PubMed, PsycINFO, Cochrane, and Web of Science for research articles investigating the effectiveness of digital mental health interventions to reduce either depression or anxiety symptoms among individuals waiting for face-to-face psychotherapy.",
    "The search was conducted in June 2024, and we have included the articles that met the inclusion criteria and were published before June 6, 2024.",
    "Results:Of the 9267 unique records identified, eight studies met the eligibility criteria and were included in the systematic review.",
    "Five studies were randomized controlled trials (RCTs), and three studies were not."
  ],
